Cancer is a disorder which has noted a significant rise in incidence worldwide 
and continues to be the largest cause of mortality. It has a dramatic impact on 
human life expectancy and quality of life in spite of the increase in technology 
and the treatments available for cancer patients. These new therapeutic options 
being chemotherapy, radiotherapy, photolytic therapy and catalytic therapy are 
known to have many adverse reactions and also no better positive outcomes than 
